Author: Jake Koenig
Summary: I tried my best. It wasn't much. I couldn't feel, so I tried to touch. I told the truth. I didn't come to fool you. And even though it all went wrong, I'll stand before the Lord of song, with nothing on my tongue, but hallelujah
